Many years ago, to provide an [age calculator gimmick](http://cloud9.hedgee.com/age) on my website, I wrote a function to calculate age to a fraction. This is a quick port of that function to C# (from [the PHP version](http://hedgee.svn.sourceforge.net/viewvc/hedgee/trunk/chris/ckwww/ckage.php3)). I'm afraid I haven't been able to test the C# version, but hope you enjoy all the same!

